Package: IGCparser
Type: Package
Title: Parse IGC files
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rohan St Hill
Maintainer: Rohan St Hill <rohan.sthill@uon.edu.au>
Description: The package can parse IGC files into; time, latitude, longitude and altitude, it also provides
    graphics to visualise the flight and calculations to find other information from the flight.
